## Third-Party Services

### Apple Services

TradeFrame integrates with the following Apple services, each governed by Apple's own privacy policies:

- **CloudKit (iCloud)** — For data synchronization across your devices
- **App Store / StoreKit** — For processing Premium subscription purchases
- **Apple Calendar (EventKit)** — For job scheduling
- **Speech Framework** — For on-device voice-to-text transcription
- **Core Location** — For GPS tagging of photos

### No Third-Party Analytics or Advertising

TradeFrame does **not** include any third-party analytics SDKs, crash reporting services, advertising frameworks, or tracking pixels. We do not use Google Analytics, Firebase, Facebook SDK, or any similar service. We do not serve ads of any kind.

