## Data Sharing

We do **not** sell, rent, trade, or otherwise share your personal data with any third party.

The only way your data leaves your device is:

1. **iCloud Sync** — Your data syncs to your personal iCloud account (managed by Apple) if you are signed in.
2. **PDFs You Share** — When you generate and share a PDF report, estimate, or invoice, you control who receives it through the iOS share sheet.
3. **CSV Exports** — When you export data as CSV files, you control where those files are sent.

In all cases, you initiate and control the sharing.

---

## Data Retention

Your data remains on your device (and in your iCloud account, if synced) for as long as you use the App. We do not have access to delete your data remotely because we do not store it.

To delete your data:

- **Delete individual records** — Remove clients, jobs, estimates, invoices, photos, or payments within the App.
- **Delete all App data** — Uninstall TradeFrame from your device. This removes all locally stored data.
- **Delete iCloud data** — Go to iOS Settings → [Your Name] → iCloud → Manage Storage → TradeFrame, and delete the data.

---

## Children's Privacy

TradeFrame is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided data through the App, please contact us so we can address it.

---

## Subscription and Payments

Premium subscriptions are processed entirely through Apple's App Store using StoreKit. We do not collect, process, or store any payment information (credit card numbers, billing addresses, etc.). All payment processing is handled by Apple under their terms and privacy policies. You can manage or cancel your subscription through iOS Settings → [Your Name] → Subscriptions.

